    "The theoretical underpinnings make the strategies generic and useful for all applications of communication.",
    "They rely on rhetorical foundations for content generation which ensures that the content developed is context-specific, addresses needs of the audience of the content, is logically accurate, useful, and meets other qualitative requirements.",
